{"tid":1992384,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【藍絲內訌】 Ideas for HK 創辦人疑似走數！創辦人莊紫祥最後竟然係想推自己條橋出黎叫人住天橋底?!","createTime":"2020-04-28T06:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T07:05:52.000Z","uid":2889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3dcd6b50b19d39216b2938dd8cda43e20f8e51bf","tid":1992384,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://vdo02.com/view2/17763/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvdo02.com%2Fview2%2F17763%2F&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=36ebc6d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://vdo02.com/view2/17763/</a><br />\n新聞來源:<a href=\"http://vdo02.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvdo02.com%2F&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=056d9860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://vdo02.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyFZe2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyFZe2v.jpg&h=349fa676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知有冇人記得Ideas for HK呢壇嘢<br />\n本身個比賽已經on9<br />\n獎金1000萬 700萬比評選員 參賽者瓜分其餘300萬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4tPCf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4tPCf3.jpg&h=eb5a16ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qTFFJV4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqTFFJV4.png&h=fe8480bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近排公佈咗冠軍<br />\n以為咁就完啦<br />\n點知創辦人莊紫祥最後竟然係想推自己條橋出黎<br />\n仲要連比評選員啲錢都疑似走數<br />\n比班藍絲屌撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hGqaAu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hGqaAu.jpg&h=db1f42f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更多笑料同影片可以去佢個網睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://pc.ideasforhk.org/#/selection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpc.ideasforhk.org%2F%23%2Fselection&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=93aa36e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pc.ideasf